          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "The desert mishkan was a portable sanctuary. Its care was guarded by the Levites and\nthe priests yet it invited all to bring their offerings. Today, we are all caretakers of\nMishkan T'filah; may our offerings be acceptable before God.\nMay all who enter find joy, solace and meaning.\nRABBI ELYSE D. FRISHMAN\nEditor\nRABBI PETER S. KNOBEL\nChair of the Editorial Committee",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
